title: Logan City School District
text:
Logan City School District is a school district located in <a href="Logan%2C%20Utah">Logan</a>, <a href="Utah">Utah</a>, <a href="United%20States">United States</a>. As its name indicates, it serves the city of Logan (while the <a href="Cache%20County%20School%20District">Cache County School District</a> serves surrounding communities within <a href="Cache%20County%2C%20Utah">Cache County</a>). It is one of 41 school districts within the state and 24th largest in terms of student enrollment.
